Hyundai to Add Third Shift at Czech Plant This Summer, WSJ Says

-- B y   S o o k y u n g   S e o
-- 
2011-02-27T22:49:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-27/hyundai-to-add-third-shift-at-czech-plant-this-summer-wsj-says.html
  Hyundai Motor Co . plans to add a
third shift at its plant in the  Czech Republic  this summer and
create 1,000 new jobs, the Wall Street Journal reported, citing
Allan Rushforth, chief operating officer for  Europe . Production
capacity at the plant will increase to 300,000 vehicles this
year, the report said.   To contact the reporter on this story:
